# Simulation Parameter Justification and Evaluation Metrics

## 3. Justification of Key Parameters

### 3.1 Number of Sessions and Simulation Time
- **Number of Sessions:** N_sessions = 10,000
- **Simulation Time:** Sessions indexed 1 to 10,000

### 3.2 Role and Policy Type Distributions
- **Role Probabilities:**
  - P(User) = 0.70
  - P(Admin) = 0.15
  - P(Fleet) = 0.15
- **Policy Type Probabilities:**
  - P(RBAC) = 0.50
  - P(ABAC) = 0.20
  - P(MAC) = 0.20
  - P(DAC) = 0.10

### 3.3 Behavior Context and Session Validity
- **Behavior Context:**
  - P(Normal) = 0.80
  - P(Anomalous) = 0.20
- **Session Validity:**
  - P(Invalid | Anomalous) = 0.08
  - P(Invalid | Normal) = 0.008

### 3.4 Time-of-Day and Attack Probability
- **Time-of-Day Probabilities:**
  - P(Morning) = 0.25
  - P(Afternoon) = 0.25
  - P(Evening) = 0.25
  - P(Off-hours) = 0.25
- **Attack Probability Modifier:**
  - P_attack(off-hours) = 1.6 × P_base
  - P_attack(evening) = 1.1 × P_base
  - P_attack(morning) = 0.8 × P_base
  - P_attack(afternoon) = 0.6 × P_base

### 3.5 Risk Score Modeling
- **Legitimate:** Risk_legit ~ N(μ_role, σ²), μ_role ∈ [0.26, 0.36], σ = 0.08
- **Malicious:** Risk_mal ~ N(μ_role, σ²), μ_role ∈ [0.75, 0.86], σ = 0.12
- **Threshold:** Access Granted if Risk Score < 0.6

### 3.6 Error Rates
- **False Acceptance Rate (FAR):**
  - FAR = False Accepts / Total Attacks
- **False Rejection Rate (FRR):**
  - FRR = False Rejects / Total Legitimate
- **With AI:** FAR_AI = 0.03, FRR_AI = 0.03
- **No AI:**
  - FAR_User = 0.07, FAR_Admin = 0.13, FAR_Fleet = 0.16
  - FRR_User = 0.03, FRR_Admin = 0.06, FRR_Fleet = 0.08

### 3.7 Latency and PET
- **Decision Latency:**
  - Latency_AI ~ N(180 ms, 25²)
  - Latency_NoAI ~ N(120 ms, 20²)
- **PET:**
  - PET_AI ~ N(80 ms, 15²)
  - PET_NoAI ~ N(60 ms, 10²)

### 3.8 Blockchain Logging Delay
- **Blockchain Delay:** Delay ~ N(200 ms, 40²)

