## 4. Metrics for Evaluation

### 4.1 Access Accuracy
- Accuracy = (True Positives + True Negatives) / Total Sessions

### 4.2 False Acceptance Rate (FAR) and False Rejection Rate (FRR)
- FAR = False Accepts / Total Attacks
- FRR = False Rejects / Total Legitimate

### 4.3 Access Denial Rate (ADR)
- ADR = Total Denied / Total Sessions

### 4.4 Risk Score Distribution
- Distribution of AI-assigned risk scores for legitimate and malicious sessions

### 4.5 Policy Type Usage
- Proportion of sessions by each policy type

### 4.6 Decision Latency and PET
- Decision Latency: Time from request to decision
- PET: Policy evaluation time

### 4.7 Blockchain Logging Delay
- Time to record decision on blockchain

### 4.8 AI Override Frequency
- % of sessions where AI overrides baseline

### 4.9 Session Validity Ratio
- Ratio of valid to invalid sessions

### 4.10 Access Decisions by Role and Behavior
- Acceptance rates by user role and behavior context

